snippet.title: Xenoblade Chronicles 3: Future Redeemed – Coming 4/25
snippet.description:
Seize the future you desire in Xenoblade Chronicles 3: Future Redeemed, coming 4/25!
This original story scenario is available exclusively via Wave 4 of the Xenoblade Chronicles 3: Expansion Pass.

https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/xenoblade-chronicles-3-expansion-pass-70070000014643-switch/
